{"tid":608091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"師奶：班賓賓都唔去拜山，點解要俾清明假佢放？","createTime":"2018-03-28T01:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T05:51:27.000Z","uid":1886,"like":12,"dislike":131,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"60921d66aa8e7d885d14426a3550a58a2fccc9ae","tid":608091,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:17:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180327/_2018032719480398792.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180327%2F_2018032719480398792.jpg&h=6ed87272&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n下周四就是清明節，不少人都會趁假期一家大小祭祖。有僱主前日於網上呻，直指香港法例過時，指清明節是給人去掃墓，「點解啲外傭又有得放假去開p，她們沒什麼墓可掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，隨即吸引網民留言，批評僱主不近人情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n有僱主前日於Facebook群組「香港外傭僱主關注組」發文，指不明白外傭在港也沒有墓可掃，為何仍可在清明節假期當日放假，讓外傭們有時間舉行派對，「僱主要拜山啲幼兒點搞，有人會帶埋去，但我不會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1175733/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1175733%2F&d=3FUI6DqlVR5Qxu5qoE%2FXcIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d4225f1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1175733%2F&h=f3179989\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1175733/</a></div>"},{"pid":"b9a79e8e995c03888b35324bf20aac370f96d242","tid":608091,"uid":12021,"like":332,"dislike":3,"score":329,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:18:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d0f2a4367228473f17d83326f46d601a6c99450","tid":608091,"uid":1886,"like":80,"dislike":2,"score":78,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:19:01.000Z","msg":"不少網民都認為該名僱主太刻薄，指清明節是法定假期，不應剝削，「帶住個B去拜山啦，畀先人見下後繼有人<img 